values:
I keep trying to type things and then when I pause to think of what to say, I fall asleep. The only thing that wakes me is lonliness and wishing to say something clever enough to elicit company.

nighto 

J

I'm very homesick. We only got one day off from our 9-6pm drawing marathon and I'm showing the apartment to prospective roommates at night...plus I still have to send back my keys for Parkway. so lame. And I need health insurance.
I can't sleep. I guess the only thing that could prepare me for this loss is this loss. I will miss you all very much. My home. My perfectly good home already.
